sentences.sentence: Will dotting toothpaste on a pimple get rid of it?
sentences.translation: 在痘痘上点涂牙膏能不能治好它？

sentences.sentence: Sometimes, it is better to remain unknown than to make pimple hate you.
sentences.translation: 有时，保持默默无闻比让人恨你要好得多。

sentences.sentence: Until then, expect pre-prom pimple conniptions to continue. —Katherine Harmon
sentences.translation: 在那之前，只能继续期待青春痘爆发提前结束。
